lce and ipe elect first trade option member the first 23 member have been elect to the joint trade option facil of the london commod exchang ( lce ) and the intern petroleum exchang ( ipe ) , the exchang said in a statement . more firm have appli and the final tranch will be admit on april one and trade is plan to start in earli june on the new trade floor on commod quay . trade option need a volatil and liquid futur base to succeed and chairman of the joint format committe jack patterson said the exist lce cocoa , coffe , sugar and ipe ga oil contract should have no difficulti in provid thi .